comments.raw_text: These are errors getting there "by design". They are expected. They don't mean anything. We could hide them, though.

comments.raw_text:
(In reply to Mike Hommey [:glandium] from comment #2)
> These are errors getting there "by design". They are expected. They don't
> mean anything. We could hide them, though.

Probably would be helpful to hide them.  Stray messages in bulk will only make it more difficult to spot real problems in the logs.
